{"tid":1007682,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"當你由去年宵市場睇開乾貨到開始鐘意睇濕貨。。。","createTime":"2019-02-04T02:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T03:46:36.000Z","uid":46801,"like":48,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"533b4f5bf7e94f6278078c7a54d1bc97453cd957","tid":1007682,"uid":46801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:51:22.000Z","msg":"代表緊已經開始變成一個大人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n讀書時期同初初做野 會約埋一大班朋友一齊行年宵市場，<br />\n<br />\n去買下野食、公仔，但從來唔會去睇年花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到做左野幾年後班fd已經各行各路，最多只係碰到面時點一下頭。<br />\n<br />\n時至今日同另一半行年宵市場已經對D 生肖公仔 、風車 、汽球已經無左興趣 。反而第一件事走左去睇年花，水仙、挑花等等<br />\n望著D花會感覺花開花落終有時，再好的緣分也會流水一樣，一去不復返。<br />\n<br />\n當見到其他人仲好青春咁將D風車同發光公仔放係個頭到 ，真係好有一種感慨 ，感慨自己已經變成一個大人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你都有同樣感覺<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你仲好年輕"},{"pid":"bdce7d1b988d4a3dd3230ee9a325e8c567ce9047","tid":1007682,"uid":77569,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:52:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da7ca67301a23e22c81f32cbca067bb7bb54f99c","tid":1007682,"uid":160147,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:52:58.000Z","msg":"唔關事 你都冇買到"},{"pid":"c2215420f401770a1708515258eda45c92e54032","tid":1007682,"uid":138197,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:53:54.000Z","msg":"濕你老母臭閪貨咩"},{"pid":"6a079a6339567853c4bc7550af78ada417123d7e","tid":1007682,"uid":127085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:54:47.000Z","msg":"挑花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6cf0f1cbbf0d4ad1723dddde0e6a213cbfbc21","tid":1007682,"uid":19932,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:56:23.000Z","msg":"幾認同，望住啲大專中學生搞年宵，賣公仔飾物抽獎，真係冇乜興致睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年行咗兩個花市，都係睇花為主，乾貨直行直過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓上話中二病嘅，應該未理會到啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過多幾年可能身同感受"},{"pid":"89cefd5042dffd6d9e7a3fe8bc9a87e22e65f9a3","tid":1007682,"uid":46801,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6a079a6339567853c4bc7550af78ada417123d7e","tid":1007682,"uid":127085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:54:47.000Z","msg":"挑花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:57:47.000Z","msg":"我打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf31eb0618ab09c797e5730b3e9f039e3d1a51d","tid":1007682,"uid":79373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:58:59.000Z","msg":"啲product買唔落手啫 最少年花都幾好睇"},{"pid":"dadf911563204363e2a30a953a5a2ca40cd3bdfa","tid":1007682,"uid":38550,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:59:26.000Z","msg":"你真係有成長就唔會去行年宵"},{"pid":"10e29e911ec0fe3c389dbffa1096d5e548d61c05","tid":1007682,"uid":59242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2215420f401770a1708515258eda45c92e54032","tid":1007682,"uid":138197,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:53:54.000Z","msg":"濕你老母臭閪貨咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:59:52.000Z","msg":"收皮啦on9 仔"},{"pid":"fd2e97bbc3f6d7b15a0fc5850fef3f904b8d0c58","tid":1007682,"uid":138197,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10e29e911ec0fe3c389dbffa1096d5e548d61c05","tid":1007682,"uid":59242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2215420f401770a1708515258eda45c92e54032","tid":1007682,"uid":138197,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:53:54.000Z","msg":"